snippet.textDisplay: Fantastic cover of one of my favorite Mountain Goats tunes. We Shall All Be Healed is such an amazing album that I feel is often overlooked as a result of following up All Hail West Texas and Tallahassee two years prior, and then The Sunset Tree a year later - three records that very frequently top peoples' list when it comes to Mountain Goats albums, leaving We Shall All Be Healed a sort of awkward middle child. Still blows my mind to this day that anyone could release four albums of such phenomenal quality over a three year period, but I guess that's The Mountain Goats for you.

snippet.textDisplay:
To any Modest Mouse Fans who play instruments (Sean included, wink wink), here’s how to play some of their easier songs which I really enjoy doing:

*I Came As A Rat*:A5, C5, G5, F5 (starts off picked, later strummed)
*Custom Concern*: C, Am, G, F
*Bankrupt on Selling*: C, Am, Em/G, F
*Styrofoam Boots*: G, Em
(One could easily make a medley of those last 3, if one were so inclined)
*Gravity Rides Everything*: A, E. ...that’s it, some strummed, some picked

Have fun everybody and thanks for the amazing shows, Sean - They really mean a lot to all of us!

My five all-time favorite songs, in order:
It's Alright Ma, I'm only Bleedin -- Bob Dylan
Outskirts of Life -- GG Allin
Galileo -- Indigo Girls
Angel of Death -- AJJ
Stoney End - Laura Nyro
Barely missing the cut--Weird Al's Everything You Know...Roger Miller's version of Little Green Apples

What I'm trying to say is... Awesome start to the quarantine stream this day. I read three book and got more than a week behind.... snippet.textDisplay: Thank you❤️🙏🏼❤️ there’s a 14 day isolated artist challenge by strussless on YouTube and one of the drawing prompts is draw a band name with one word( or in your case letter) replaced with the word hand sanitizer so yup- AHANDSANITIZERJ is my pick🤩 but I don’t draw very well so I think I’ll paint it😃 he also mentions you guys on a few videos which is what made me watch more☀️☀️☀️ thank you seriously sooo flipping much for entertaining and lifting spirits during these times❤️🙏🏼❤️ over a week ago my partner and I decided to take us and our 2 year old daughter to my mom and brothers Incase we got locked down and on a positive note, I’m totally digging being cooped up with the ones I love😍❤️😍 we never get to do it but in times of crisis you want to be with your loved ones- the ones that remind you life IS worth all the garbage-y garbage that exists❤️ my Christmas present from my partner this past year was tickets to your Cleveland show in May and I was going to get a sitter so we could get tickets to the Detroit show the day before the CLE show but maybe it’ll happen still🤩🤞🏼🤩 if not these shows online have made up for it😍😍😍 I got to watch u guys live, on a back porch in friggin West Virginia, with my MOM😍❤️😍😂😂 she like Huey Lewis and Dwight Yokam so it’s something that never would have been in my experience if this crazy shit didn’t happen so there’s my silver lining- thank you❤️🙏🏼❤️☀️☀️☀️☀️🤟🏼🤟🏼🤟🏼
